<h1>The chloroquine chronicles: A history of the drug that conquered the world</h1>
<div class="panel-pane pane-entity-field pane-node-field-teaser" >
  
      
  
  
  <p class="field-teaser">
    The history of the antimalarial drug chloroquine has many lessons about the power — and geopolitics — of medicine.   </p>

  
  </div>

  <p class="field-ref-program story__program story__meta">
    <a href="/programs/the-world">The World</a>  </p>

  <p class="field-date-published story__meta">
    <span class="date-display-single" property="dc:date" datatype="xsd:dateTime" content="2020-04-15T13:30:00-04:00">April 15, 2020 · 1:30 PM EDT</span>  </p>

  <div class="field-fc-story-creators story__meta">
    
  By
  <a href="/people/elana-gordon">Elana Gordon</a>  </div>
